'''Jabba's marker''' was a gold coin that indicated the customer was under the employ of [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]. Though primarily a device for extortion rather than monetary value, the coin advertised the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt's]] wealth to those who saw it.

